SUMMARY:602 planning [@mtg]
DESCRIPTION:1. looked for Fall 2025 SRTI feedback in TEAMS folder\, but was
  empty.\n   Sent email [2026-06-17 Wed] to Lisa Groth asking about this.\n
 2. ☐ look for videos on Youtube\, etc instead of or as a complement to\n  
  our own\n3. 2 EA\, 2 presentations\, 2 FR\n   • ☐ how to penalize student
 s who are unprepared?\n4. Yes to share older reports and extended abstract
 s as examples\n5. 6 labs with 5 groups provides slack time and flexibility
 \n   1. contact angle goniometer camera has failed.  Check in with\n      
 Hayden Marquard.\n6. Equipment status:\n   1. light scattering\n   2. elec
 tron microscopy\n   3. rheology\n   4. ☐ x-ray\n   5. ☐ surface analysis /
  contact angle\n   6. ☐ *calorimetry*: TGA\, DSC\n7. Find TAs!
